    "options_maxZoomAllowed_percentageExplanation": {
        "message": "This value is used by <b>Grow Only</b> and <b>Shrink And Grow</b> modes to calculate the maximum size to which the contents may be enlarged. As a general rule this is the maximum zoom level that the screen supports without showing the horizontal scrollbar. In case horizontal scrollbar is showed, even when window is maximized, decreased this value until it disappears.",
